---
import { Picture } from "astro:assets";

import alnImg from "@/assets/images/aln.png"
import curaFest from "@/assets/images/gycuraFest.png"
---

    <header class="relative w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-10 md:py-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        
        <div class="relative z-10 space-y-6">
            <div class="absolute -top-10 left-0 transform -rotate-6 hidden md:block">
                <span class="font-hand text-ale-orange text-2xl">¡Solo para Hermosillo!</span>
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-ale-orange inline-block ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 14l-7 7m0 0l-7-7m7 7V3"></path></svg>
            </div>

            <!-- FOTO DIPUTADA (NUEVO) -->
            <!-- Sustituye el src por la foto real de la diputada (ej. foto-alejandra.png) -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="relative group cursor-pointer">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-ale-pink rounded-full blur opacity-30 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-300"></div>
                            <Picture
                                src={alnImg}
                                alt={"Diputada Alejandra López Noriega"}
                                width={500}
                                height={500}
                                class=`relative size-24 md:w-28 md:h-28 rounded-full 
                                border-4 border-white shadow-xl object-cover 
                                transform transition group-hover:scale-105`
                                formats={["avif", "webp"]}
                            />
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Burbuja de diálogo opcional -->
                <div class="bg-white px-4 py-2 rounded-xl rounded-tl-none shadow-md border border-gray-100 transform rotate-2 hidden sm:block">
                    <p class="font-hand text-ale-pink font-bold text-lg">¡Hola, te invito a participar!</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-ale-purple leading-tight">
                GANA 2 BOLETOS <br>
                <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-linear-to-r from-ale-pink to-ale-orange">VIP CURA FEST</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 font-medium">
                Esta Navidad quiero consentirte. Participa para ver a <strong class="text-ale-purple">Carín León</strong> desde la zona <span class="bg-yellow-100 text-ale-orange px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border-b-2 border-ale-orange">VIP Boca Chueca 1</span> totalmente gratis.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 pt-4">
                <a href="#registro" class="btn-hover bg-ale-orange text-white text-center px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold text-lg shadow-lg uppercase tracking-wide w-full sm:w-auto">
                    ¡Quiero Participar!
                </a>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-ale-purple font-hand font-black text-2xl">
                    <span>👑</span>
                    <span>Sorteo: 6 de Enero</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

<div class="relative group">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-full h-full bg-ale-pink/10 rounded-[3rem] transform rotate-3 scale-105 z-0"></div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 bg-white p-4 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl border-4 border-ale-pink/20 rotate-[-2deg] transition-transform duration-300 hover:rotate-0">
        
        <div class="bg-gray-900 h-64 md:h-80 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden group">
            
            <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-ale-orange z-10"></div>

            <Picture
                src={curaFest}
                alt={"Giveaway Cura Fest"}
                width={1000}
                height={640}
                class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover z-0"
                formats={["avif", "webp"]}
            />

            <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-32 h-32 bg-ale-pink rounded-full opacity-20 blur-xl z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4 text-center">
            <p class="font-hand text-ale-purple text-xl">"El mejor regalo para cerrar el año"</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <svg class="absolute -bottom-16 -left-14 w-24 h-24 text-ale-purple transform -rotate-12 hidden md:block" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path></svg>
</div>
    </header>